_struct_biol.details   
;The biological assembly is a trimer generated from the monomer    
in the asymmetric unit by applying the transformation matrices:   
rotation-1:    
| 1  0  0|   
| 0  1  0|   
| 0  0  1|   
translation-1:   
(0 0 0 )  
 
rotation-2:    
|-0.5 -0.866 0|   
|0.866 -0.5  0|   
| 0   0   1|   
translation-2:   
(54.29 0 0 )  
and   
rotation-3:    
|-0.5  0.866  0|   
|-0.866 -0.5  0|   
| 0   0   1|   
translation-3:   
(27.3 47.28 0 )
;
